subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: Building of national institutions to plan for, monitor and evaluate the use of national resources is primary objective for the project, through sectors. Support will also be provided to increase management of aid effectiveness and sharing of information for all development partners. The generation of timely and needed information will also be supported for the central statistic office. All the undertaking will be guided by the national global MDG objectives.
subproject.title: Strengthening National Capacit

title: Strengthening National Capacities for Poverty Reduction
